<a class="simple-item-image item-image" href="/news-politics/politics/a27042848/alexandria-ocasio-cortez-paul-ryan-advice/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Transporter" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="AOC Has at Least 3 Reasons to Ignore Paul Ryan" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.esquire.com/news-politics/politics/a27042848/alexandria-ocasio-cortez-paul-ryan-advice/" data-vars-ga-position="4" data-vars-ga-total-positions="11">
						
